A plain text version of this hypertext document is in the
file SpamFryer.text. Apart from the links and formatting, the
content of both files is the same. This AmigaGuide version is
for people who like to click their way though an electronic
document, with cross-references and an automated index. The
plain text suits those who prefer to refer to a printout, or be
sure they've read everything. An HTML version is also available,
for those who prefer to read things in a Web browser.

@ENDNODE
